WEBVTT

00:01:15.700 --> 00:01:20.940
=About Love=

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.940
=Episode 9=

00:01:54.150 --> 00:01:55.870
Did you call these people over today?

00:01:56.480 --> 00:01:57.510
What people?

00:01:57.950 --> 00:01:59.150
Is there some misunderstanding?

00:01:59.710 --> 00:02:00.790
Just spit it out.

00:02:01.560 --> 00:02:04.120
I haven't seen you in ages,
so I miss you so much.

00:02:04.680 --> 00:02:05.870
And I'm dying to know

00:02:06.400 --> 00:02:07.590
what kind of

00:02:07.590 --> 00:02:08.960
boyfriend you got?

00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:14.590
I'll bring him to meet you
in a couple of days.

00:02:15.560 --> 00:02:16.400
That sounds great.

00:02:16.470 --> 00:02:18.520
I've been free lately. Come anytime.

00:02:32.300 --> 00:02:36.820
(Bei)

00:02:38.280 --> 00:02:39.630
Are you gonna call him?

00:02:44.030 --> 00:02:45.960
You wanna tell him everything about me?

00:02:47.150 --> 00:02:48.120
Think carefully.

00:02:49.360 --> 00:02:51.710
He might be at
another woman's place right now.

00:02:55.960 --> 00:02:58.000
Do you really think
he can understand me?

00:02:59.360 --> 00:03:00.710
Do you even know him that well?

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:06.430
Who is he calling today?

00:03:07.890 --> 00:03:08.730
It's already so late.

00:03:08.750 --> 00:03:10.000
Why does he have to go see her?

00:03:11.590 --> 00:03:13.150
Do you know his past?

00:03:14.400 --> 00:03:15.240
Tell me,

00:03:15.470 --> 00:03:17.240
will he be just like other guys?

00:03:18.400 --> 00:03:20.120
Stop dodging my question. Look at me.

00:03:21.590 --> 00:03:22.840
Look at me!

00:03:24.710 --> 00:03:26.910
Before you figure out
who he's actually meeting,

00:03:27.560 --> 00:03:28.630
don't tell him anything.

00:03:29.030 --> 00:03:29.870
Most importantly,

00:03:30.120 --> 00:03:31.240
never let anyone

00:03:31.520 --> 00:03:33.030
tell him about me.

00:03:37.300 --> 00:03:40.060
(Bei)

00:03:40.960 --> 00:03:41.960
Don't hesitate.

00:04:07.430 --> 00:04:08.590
Hello, Guan.

00:04:10.430 --> 00:04:11.590
Let's make it tonight.

00:04:12.750 --> 00:04:14.470
Do you two keep in touch privately?

00:04:15.190 --> 00:04:16.560
Only when necessary.

00:04:16.750 --> 00:04:17.800
I got nothing to hide.

00:04:18.040 --> 00:04:19.360
Then why not tell Bei?

00:04:19.710 --> 00:04:20.550
Do I need to check in

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:21.870
with Xiu when I shop with you?

00:04:22.070 --> 00:04:23.190
You're no different from me.

00:04:23.680 --> 00:04:24.750
Shoving our own logic

00:04:24.830 --> 00:04:25.950
down others' throats.

00:04:26.360 --> 00:04:28.510
The difference between us is

00:04:29.830 --> 00:04:31.720
I know how to follow my heart

00:04:31.830 --> 00:04:32.920
without crossing lines.

00:04:40.300 --> 00:04:41.540
(Jiang Yifan)

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:46.640
Hello.

00:04:47.390 --> 00:04:49.390
Got any plans tonight?

00:04:51.310 --> 00:04:52.160
Yeah.

00:04:53.310 --> 00:04:54.310
Just kidding.

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:56.560
Silly, I'll go with your plan.

00:04:57.750 --> 00:04:59.070
Can you come over?

00:04:59.800 --> 00:05:00.650
Sure.

00:05:00.720 --> 00:05:01.600
Wait for me.

00:05:03.190 --> 00:05:04.030
Her?

00:05:04.390 --> 00:05:05.230
Ah.

00:05:06.920 --> 00:05:07.760
Go on then.

00:05:15.720 --> 00:05:17.310
Do you think having a kindred person

00:05:17.680 --> 00:05:18.800
makes you less lonely?

00:05:19.070 --> 00:05:20.120
I don't need one.

00:05:20.220 --> 00:05:21.240
Besides, things like this.

00:05:21.270 --> 00:05:22.870
No one can ease this guilt of mine.

00:05:23.720 --> 00:05:25.480
I just enjoy seeing people fall in love.

00:05:25.950 --> 00:05:27.630
No matter who. No matter what bond.

00:05:29.160 --> 00:05:30.600
Then I might let you down.

00:05:31.120 --> 00:05:31.960
Stop pretending.

00:05:32.360 --> 00:05:33.430
I know you're in love.

00:05:33.720 --> 00:05:35.070
This is the kind of love you want.

00:05:35.800 --> 00:05:36.720
Crazy.

00:05:37.190 --> 00:05:39.190
Take care of my little fairy. Bye.

00:06:42.480 --> 00:06:43.360
Mingming.

00:06:44.040 --> 00:06:45.070
Turn your body a little.

00:06:45.570 --> 00:06:46.560
No need to lift your head.

00:06:47.360 --> 00:06:48.200
Yeah.

00:06:51.240 --> 00:06:52.360
Hold on.

00:06:54.040 --> 00:06:54.920
I think we're

00:06:55.200 --> 00:06:56.270
moving too fast, aren't we?

00:06:56.830 --> 00:06:57.670
Not really.

00:06:58.160 --> 00:06:59.680
We're officially a couple now.

00:07:00.000 --> 00:07:01.390
Yeah.

00:07:01.510 --> 00:07:02.430
But I still feel...

00:07:02.800 --> 00:07:03.750
a little nervous.

00:07:03.760 --> 00:07:04.600
I came here planning to

00:07:04.610 --> 00:07:05.560
give myself to you,

00:07:05.560 --> 00:07:06.400
but

00:07:06.690 --> 00:07:07.590
I think maybe we

00:07:07.600 --> 00:07:08.480
need to get closer.

00:07:08.560 --> 00:07:09.950
Aren't we close enough already?

00:07:10.390 --> 00:07:11.230
Mingming,

00:07:11.270 --> 00:07:13.160
we're officially together today.

00:07:14.000 --> 00:07:14.870
Relax, okay?

00:07:15.480 --> 00:07:16.750
Just give me a bit more time.

00:07:17.000 --> 00:07:18.480
I've already given you so much.

00:07:18.920 --> 00:07:19.760
Mingming,

00:07:19.950 --> 00:07:21.190
I really like you.

00:07:22.360 --> 00:07:23.390
Sen, stop!

00:07:23.580 --> 00:07:24.750
Keep going, and I'll get mad.

00:07:24.950 --> 00:07:25.950
Why?

00:07:26.240 --> 00:07:27.920
You're the one who asked for it tonight.

00:07:28.500 --> 00:07:29.510
It'll be quick, Mingming.

00:07:30.360 --> 00:07:31.950
Sen, Sen!

00:07:39.240 --> 00:07:40.680
Are... are you okay?

00:07:41.300 --> 00:07:42.720
You're still thinking about him, right?

00:07:44.480 --> 00:07:45.510
I'm not.

00:07:47.310 --> 00:07:48.750
I know I can't compare to him.

00:07:49.280 --> 00:07:51.270
I know girls only give themselves
to someone they love.

00:07:51.720 --> 00:07:53.070
Whether you're their boyfriend or not.

00:07:53.120 --> 00:07:53.960
Don't say that.

00:07:54.430 --> 00:07:55.720
Did I say something wrong?

00:07:56.620 --> 00:07:58.000
Honestly, I'm just jealous of him.

00:07:58.160 --> 00:07:59.870
He's already
taken over your heart completely.

00:08:00.630 --> 00:08:01.800
You wanted it with him.

00:08:01.970 --> 00:08:03.750
But when I touch you,
everything feels off.

00:08:03.830 --> 00:08:05.310
It's not like that.

00:08:06.800 --> 00:08:07.870
He respected me at first.

00:08:08.000 --> 00:08:08.950
When we were in bed…

00:08:09.070 --> 00:08:10.630
Don't talk about that!

00:08:24.390 --> 00:08:25.600
Stop messing around, okay?

00:08:27.720 --> 00:08:29.390
Today's our first official day together.

00:08:29.510 --> 00:08:31.510
I don't wanna fight over this.

00:08:33.510 --> 00:08:34.350
Sorry.

00:08:36.200 --> 00:08:37.630
I didn't respect you enough.

00:08:38.670 --> 00:08:39.670
I apologize.

00:08:39.830 --> 00:08:40.720
Sen.

00:08:40.840 --> 00:08:41.790
You… you sleep first.

00:08:41.840 --> 00:08:43.630
I'll… I'll wait in the living room.

00:09:04.630 --> 00:09:05.480
Hello.

00:09:05.720 --> 00:09:07.240
Have we met before?

00:09:09.200 --> 00:09:10.080
Who are you?

00:09:10.910 --> 00:09:12.000
I'm your husband.

00:09:12.390 --> 00:09:13.840
From another parallel universe.

00:09:14.000 --> 00:09:15.080
We have two cute daughters.

00:09:15.200 --> 00:09:16.270
And a pet dog.

00:09:16.510 --> 00:09:18.720
One day,
you left home with just a letter behind.

00:09:18.800 --> 00:09:19.840
You said the world's vast.

00:09:20.320 --> 00:09:22.320
And you wanted to find a lamppost.

00:09:22.340 --> 00:09:23.480
Why are you dressed like this?

00:09:24.150 --> 00:09:25.630
Didn't you tell me to dress formally?

00:09:26.150 --> 00:09:26.990
Alright.

00:09:27.200 --> 00:09:28.870
Just don't carry that shark bag.

00:09:33.750 --> 00:09:34.960
So, what do you want?

00:09:35.840 --> 00:09:36.720
Be my boyfriend.

00:09:39.910 --> 00:09:41.480
You mean this Aunt Guan

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:42.910
is threatening you with Bei?

00:09:46.440 --> 00:09:47.870
Then just give Bei to her.

00:09:48.200 --> 00:09:49.320
He's not worth much.

00:09:49.570 --> 00:09:50.790
Sir, please put your feet down.

00:09:51.050 --> 00:09:52.240
200 yuan if you dirty the car.

00:09:58.270 --> 00:09:59.720
She's really scheming.

00:10:00.390 --> 00:10:02.510
She'll try every way to slander my past.

00:10:02.910 --> 00:10:04.910
That'd definitely be
beyond Bei's tolerance.

00:10:05.390 --> 00:10:07.360
Actually, no man would
be able to handle that.

00:10:08.670 --> 00:10:09.510
Maybe

00:10:09.910 --> 00:10:11.200
someone can accept it.

00:10:13.720 --> 00:10:15.750
Now I get what "words can kill" means.

00:10:18.510 --> 00:10:20.440
She called those people today, right?

00:10:20.670 --> 00:10:21.510
Mhm.

00:10:22.200 --> 00:10:23.240
She's warning me.

00:10:34.550 --> 00:10:35.510
Take this with you.

00:10:35.870 --> 00:10:37.630
It might come in handy
if you're in trouble.

00:10:38.000 --> 00:10:39.080
No matter how deep their love,

00:10:39.270 --> 00:10:41.150
they can't guard you round the clock.

00:10:41.600 --> 00:10:43.670
When danger hits,
we can only rely on ourselves.

00:10:45.670 --> 00:10:46.510
Thanks.

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:52.080
As for Aunt Guan,

00:10:52.960 --> 00:10:54.440
let me be the one to deal with her.

00:10:55.720 --> 00:10:57.270
With a guy this perfect,

00:10:57.670 --> 00:10:59.390
I wanna see
what trouble she can stir up.

00:10:59.720 --> 00:11:00.600
One more thing.

00:11:00.720 --> 00:11:01.580
For real,

00:11:01.630 --> 00:11:03.670
I'm only here to perform,
not sell myself.

00:11:04.140 --> 00:11:05.080
Can you tell me

00:11:05.200 --> 00:11:06.670
what's Bei's ex-girlfriend's name?

00:11:06.870 --> 00:11:08.200
Betray a friend isn't okay either.

00:11:08.350 --> 00:11:09.300
So you're on good terms

00:11:09.320 --> 00:11:10.750
with all his exes.

00:11:10.840 --> 00:11:12.000
Stop joking.

00:11:12.790 --> 00:11:15.240
I'm not close to any of his exes.

00:11:16.120 --> 00:11:17.480
Then it's not betraying a friend.

00:11:19.320 --> 00:11:21.270
Your logic is wild.

00:11:22.150 --> 00:11:23.320
Tell me, please?

00:11:23.750 --> 00:11:24.790
I'm just curious.

00:11:25.840 --> 00:11:27.790
I know nothing about Bei's past.

00:11:28.870 --> 00:11:29.840
If you won't tell me,

00:11:29.960 --> 00:11:31.150
I'll ask someone else.

00:11:31.510 --> 00:11:32.550
I'll find out eventually.

00:11:33.120 --> 00:11:33.960
Hmm.

00:11:34.200 --> 00:11:36.120
Good point, you'll find out eventually.

00:11:36.840 --> 00:11:38.270
But I'll never tell you.

00:11:38.810 --> 00:11:40.600
But if you wanna delete two words

00:11:40.750 --> 00:11:42.000
from the dictionary,

00:11:42.390 --> 00:11:43.390
I can recommend one.

00:11:44.320 --> 00:11:45.840
Zhen Guan.

00:11:47.030 --> 00:11:48.150
His ex is Zhen Guan?

00:11:48.270 --> 00:11:50.390
That is the name of his shop, Sis!

00:11:50.510 --> 00:11:52.200
He's a workaholic.

00:11:52.480 --> 00:11:54.270
Your rival is definitely his job.

00:11:58.330 --> 00:11:59.320
Which building was it again?

00:11:59.630 --> 00:12:01.840
Building 5, Unit 7, Room 419.

00:12:01.900 --> 00:12:03.030
I left the door open for you.

00:12:03.200 --> 00:12:04.550
Don't leave it open. It's not safe.

00:12:04.910 --> 00:12:07.030
Who makes it unsafe? You?

00:12:07.320 --> 00:12:08.840
If I'm really in danger,

00:12:09.270 --> 00:12:10.480
will you come save the day?

00:12:10.960 --> 00:12:12.440
You haven't changed at all.

00:12:12.670 --> 00:12:13.670
Who says I haven't?

00:12:13.910 --> 00:12:15.030
I'm getting prettier.

00:12:15.360 --> 00:12:16.440
Okay, I'm almost there.

00:12:18.670 --> 00:12:19.510
Here.

00:12:20.080 --> 00:12:21.080
Are you ready?

00:12:22.240 --> 00:12:23.200
Of course.

00:12:25.480 --> 00:12:27.030
I'm a pro at playing boyfriend.

00:12:27.120 --> 00:12:28.670
Need any foreplay?

00:12:29.360 --> 00:12:30.670
What I meant was…

00:12:31.480 --> 00:12:32.630
Could you…

00:12:32.630 --> 00:12:34.030
Hmm? What's wrong?

00:12:34.030 --> 00:12:35.030
Play him.

00:12:38.390 --> 00:12:39.230
Him?

00:12:41.000 --> 00:12:42.240
I'm even better at playing him.

00:12:42.320 --> 00:12:43.600
You'll see later.

00:12:43.910 --> 00:12:45.030
Just worried I might

00:12:45.030 --> 00:12:46.030
get too into it.

00:12:48.030 --> 00:12:48.870
Let's go.

00:13:38.910 --> 00:13:40.270
Our Xiaoxi

00:13:40.440 --> 00:13:42.240
finally has time to see me.

00:13:42.910 --> 00:13:43.960
I've been so busy lately.

00:13:44.100 --> 00:13:45.200
Today I happened to have time

00:13:45.320 --> 00:13:47.240
to visit you with my boyfriend.

00:13:48.440 --> 00:13:49.360
This is Guan.

00:13:50.000 --> 00:13:51.360
Hello, Guan, I'm…

00:13:51.550 --> 00:13:54.030
Young man, you're really something.

00:13:54.240 --> 00:13:56.390
You even managed to win over Xiaoxi.

00:13:57.670 --> 00:13:59.750
But Xiaoxi has good taste.

00:14:00.030 --> 00:14:01.240
After all that choosing,

00:14:01.840 --> 00:14:02.840
you're truly quite the catch.

00:14:03.000 --> 00:14:04.600
You're flattering me, Guan.

00:14:04.870 --> 00:14:07.080
Xiaoxi's always telling me
how amazing you are.

00:14:07.150 --> 00:14:08.720
I should've visited you ages ago.

00:14:09.030 --> 00:14:11.080
Seeing is believing.

00:14:11.270 --> 00:14:12.790
Look at Guan, she's so well-maintained.

00:14:13.030 --> 00:14:15.200
Don't look a day over 20,

00:14:15.390 --> 00:14:16.600
more like 17 or 18.

00:14:18.840 --> 00:14:20.030
Come on, have a seat.

00:14:28.510 --> 00:14:29.390
An Miu.

00:14:32.960 --> 00:14:33.800
Where are you?

00:14:35.630 --> 00:14:38.240
Bei, did you miss me?

00:14:39.120 --> 00:14:40.200
Come down first.

00:14:41.810 --> 00:14:43.390
Can't believe it's been so long. You've…

00:14:44.080 --> 00:14:45.510
You've gained weight.

00:14:46.550 --> 00:14:47.910
Can you talk?

00:14:48.750 --> 00:14:50.720
Would it kill you to say I got prettier?

00:14:51.200 --> 00:14:52.240
Ah, fine, you're prettier.

00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:53.160
Happy now? Prettier.

00:14:53.230 --> 00:14:54.120
Too late.

00:14:54.140 --> 00:14:55.440
Think about how to make it up to me.

00:14:55.630 --> 00:14:57.200
Well, I brought your favorite crawfish.

00:14:57.510 --> 00:14:59.030
So, what's your name, young man?

00:14:59.320 --> 00:15:00.240
My last name's Bao.

00:15:00.360 --> 00:15:01.360
Given name is Bei.

00:15:01.600 --> 00:15:03.270
You can call me Angela.

00:15:03.550 --> 00:15:04.790
That name sounds pretty cool.

00:15:06.440 --> 00:15:07.790
Your name suits you.

00:15:08.910 --> 00:15:10.120
You flatter me, Guan.

00:15:10.910 --> 00:15:13.150
My dad loved foreign classic literature.

00:15:13.390 --> 00:15:14.440
When he picked my name,

00:15:14.440 --> 00:15:16.000
he borrowed it
from a character in a book.

00:15:16.480 --> 00:15:18.840
Was it Huckleberry or Isabella?

00:15:21.600 --> 00:15:22.840
Vegeta.

00:15:24.340 --> 00:15:25.290
You know, the short guy

00:15:25.390 --> 00:15:26.790
with a receding hairline.

00:15:27.960 --> 00:15:28.870
Back then, my dad

00:15:28.870 --> 00:15:30.630
probably thought I wasn't born a prince,

00:15:30.910 --> 00:15:33.000
but I should have the heart to
win a princess.

00:15:33.480 --> 00:15:34.320
Luckily,

00:15:34.960 --> 00:15:36.720
I didn't let him down.

00:15:46.000 --> 00:15:46.910
Don't mind him, Guan.

00:15:47.030 --> 00:15:48.440
He just likes joking around.

00:15:49.440 --> 00:15:50.750
He's pretty funny.

00:15:52.000 --> 00:15:53.030
Where do you work now?

00:15:53.270 --> 00:15:54.910
Just scraping by at an appraisal shop.

00:15:56.000 --> 00:15:56.840
What do you appraise?

00:15:57.120 --> 00:15:57.960
Everything.

00:15:58.100 --> 00:15:59.550
Breast augmentations,
nose jobs, eye lifts.

00:15:59.700 --> 00:16:01.250
Jaw reshaping, bone shaving,
silicone implants.

00:16:01.480 --> 00:16:03.630
I can spot them at a glance.

00:16:07.320 --> 00:16:09.000
What about me, then?

00:16:10.790 --> 00:16:11.910
Guan.

00:16:12.670 --> 00:16:14.240
You've still got charm.

00:16:14.670 --> 00:16:15.600
You wear your years well.

00:16:15.840 --> 00:16:17.510
Your beauty feels so genuine.

00:16:18.360 --> 00:16:19.320
But these days,

00:16:19.630 --> 00:16:21.030
I don't appraise faces anymore.

00:16:21.270 --> 00:16:22.550
Mostly appraise cowhide, sheepskin,

00:16:22.670 --> 00:16:23.840
pigskin and so on.

00:16:24.720 --> 00:16:26.030
Guan must have plenty, right?

00:16:27.480 --> 00:16:28.320
Don't get me wrong.

00:16:28.510 --> 00:16:29.600
I mean

00:16:30.240 --> 00:16:31.630
bags made of those materials.

00:16:33.240 --> 00:16:35.240
I have a few. Maybe

00:16:35.430 --> 00:16:36.630
you can appraise them sometime.

00:16:36.840 --> 00:16:37.790
My pleasure.

00:16:38.080 --> 00:16:38.960
But

00:16:39.630 --> 00:16:42.080
if I find a few fakes,

00:16:42.440 --> 00:16:44.030
don't take it to heart.

00:16:44.670 --> 00:16:45.670
In this lifetime,

00:16:45.840 --> 00:16:47.200
who hasn't bought a fake

00:16:47.550 --> 00:16:48.910
or met a jerk?

00:16:49.750 --> 00:16:50.590
You know what I mean.

00:16:51.200 --> 00:16:52.040
Right?

00:16:53.270 --> 00:16:54.110
Yeah.

00:16:55.550 --> 00:16:57.750
Looks like you're
planning to settle down.

00:16:58.200 --> 00:16:59.040
- Ah?
- Mm.

00:16:59.240 --> 00:17:00.150
I'm not drinking.

00:17:02.630 --> 00:17:03.600
Actually, I'd already

00:17:03.750 --> 00:17:05.790
secretly found a place
online beforehand,

00:17:06.000 --> 00:17:07.110
wanted to surprise you.

00:17:07.510 --> 00:17:09.640
But I couldn't hold back
after moving in.

00:17:09.690 --> 00:17:10.790
So I called you right away.

00:17:14.350 --> 00:17:15.200
Thanks.

00:17:17.550 --> 00:17:18.830
I've been meaning to ask.

00:17:19.350 --> 00:17:20.510
Weren't you studying law?

00:17:20.790 --> 00:17:21.880
Why go into entertainment news?

00:17:22.030 --> 00:17:24.160
I wanna interview
my favorite celebrities.

00:17:24.240 --> 00:17:25.080
Oh.

00:17:25.680 --> 00:17:27.320
Let me give you
a little exclusive scoop.

00:17:27.320 --> 00:17:28.210
How about that?

00:17:28.270 --> 00:17:29.480
Next week, Mianmian is gonna

00:17:29.550 --> 00:17:31.350
announce her relationship
on a variety show.

00:17:31.480 --> 00:17:32.320
You know Mo Yue?

00:17:32.590 --> 00:17:34.750
She's switching to
comedy movies next year.

00:17:39.480 --> 00:17:41.000
Do you not know any of these people?

00:17:41.440 --> 00:17:42.480
Not a single one.

00:17:42.960 --> 00:17:44.030
I don't follow that stuff.

00:17:44.270 --> 00:17:45.920
Your life is so boring!

00:17:46.510 --> 00:17:48.240
Isn't it illegal to write about

00:17:48.920 --> 00:17:49.760
people's privacy?

00:17:50.000 --> 00:17:50.840
Mm.

00:17:51.340 --> 00:17:52.750
It depends on what kind.

00:17:54.550 --> 00:17:58.000
Article 55 of
the Personality Rights Law.

00:17:58.400 --> 00:18:00.200
For public interest,

00:18:00.350 --> 00:18:02.070
we can conduct media supervision

00:18:02.590 --> 00:18:03.880
and appropriately disclose

00:18:04.000 --> 00:18:06.000
public figures' privacy.

00:18:06.110 --> 00:18:08.680
The supervised party can't claim

00:18:08.880 --> 00:18:10.000
infringement.

00:18:10.480 --> 00:18:12.200
All that law school wasn't for nothing.

00:18:12.720 --> 00:18:14.880
They have high-profile jobs.

00:18:14.880 --> 00:18:15.740
It's impossible

00:18:15.740 --> 00:18:17.550
to only show
what they want people to see.

00:18:17.660 --> 00:18:18.510
So you're saying,

00:18:18.510 --> 00:18:19.960
you're actually
playing a supervisor role?

00:18:20.680 --> 00:18:21.790
Not that noble.

00:18:22.000 --> 00:18:23.550
We're just giving people what they want.

00:18:27.920 --> 00:18:28.760
What's wrong?

00:18:28.960 --> 00:18:30.030
I was just thinking...

00:18:31.160 --> 00:18:32.350
Forget celebrities,

00:18:33.160 --> 00:18:34.160
even regular folks,

00:18:34.270 --> 00:18:35.510
I bet most can't

00:18:35.750 --> 00:18:37.680
put their private life on full display

00:18:38.160 --> 00:18:39.350
and still
walk away unscathed.

00:18:40.590 --> 00:18:41.480
Who says it's impossible?

00:18:43.240 --> 00:18:44.270
You are.

00:18:54.000 --> 00:18:56.240
(Guan, we're here now.)

00:19:03.070 --> 00:19:04.070
Mr. Bao.

00:19:05.880 --> 00:19:08.440
Please treat our Xiaoxi well.

00:19:08.880 --> 00:19:09.720
Yeah.

00:19:10.240 --> 00:19:11.240
Don't dwell on

00:19:11.880 --> 00:19:13.440
her unnecessary past.

00:19:14.030 --> 00:19:15.240
We may

00:19:15.510 --> 00:19:18.030
never know the truth about something.

00:19:19.000 --> 00:19:20.720
Her stories

00:19:21.000 --> 00:19:21.840
with men.

00:19:22.200 --> 00:19:23.480
There are countless versions.

00:19:24.590 --> 00:19:26.110
But remember.

00:19:26.590 --> 00:19:27.430
Those

00:19:27.680 --> 00:19:29.110
were all just flings.

00:19:30.880 --> 00:19:31.830
I think with you,

00:19:32.920 --> 00:19:34.400
she's serious.

00:19:39.960 --> 00:19:40.800
Guan.

00:19:43.720 --> 00:19:45.160
Since we're on the subject,

00:19:45.270 --> 00:19:46.310
I'll be honest.

00:19:47.070 --> 00:19:48.160
Can I talk to someone?

00:19:48.510 --> 00:19:50.440
I'm really bottled up inside.

00:19:51.790 --> 00:19:53.110
I fell for Xiaoxi

00:19:53.680 --> 00:19:55.510
because she's innocent and pure.

00:19:56.030 --> 00:19:57.590
Like a newborn calf.

00:19:58.130 --> 00:19:58.970
Then one day,

00:19:59.000 --> 00:20:00.680
she told me about her past.

00:20:00.880 --> 00:20:02.510
I didn't wanna hear it, really.

00:20:02.790 --> 00:20:04.350
I didn't wanna know at all.

00:20:06.400 --> 00:20:07.400
But Guan,

00:20:08.350 --> 00:20:09.480
you don't know me well.

00:20:10.160 --> 00:20:13.000
I was born into a scholarly family.

00:20:13.550 --> 00:20:14.410
My parents

00:20:14.440 --> 00:20:16.440
are very traditional intellectuals.

00:20:16.790 --> 00:20:19.440
And I'm the only son
of nine generations.

00:20:20.270 --> 00:20:21.240
They'd never let me

00:20:21.510 --> 00:20:23.200
marry a girl like Xiaoxi.

00:20:24.310 --> 00:20:25.350
Think about it.

00:20:26.830 --> 00:20:29.270
She's pure and graceful,

00:20:30.070 --> 00:20:31.790
yet simply because she's beautiful,

00:20:32.270 --> 00:20:35.070
she became a test
for countless scumbags!

00:20:36.750 --> 00:20:40.000
The mastermind behind this is shameless.

00:20:40.400 --> 00:20:42.310
I can't imagine

00:20:43.240 --> 00:20:46.000
how much injustice
such a kind girl has endured.

00:20:46.310 --> 00:20:47.550
Who knows?

00:20:48.270 --> 00:20:49.480
Who cares?

00:20:52.750 --> 00:20:53.880
Only me.

00:20:56.510 --> 00:20:58.000
And unbelievably,

00:20:58.070 --> 00:20:59.680
someone even showed up
demanding "love debts".

00:21:00.000 --> 00:21:01.200
Good thing I was there at the time.

00:21:01.310 --> 00:21:02.150
In a flash,

00:21:02.510 --> 00:21:03.920
I took care of him on the spot.

00:21:04.160 --> 00:21:05.550
Before that day, I never thought

00:21:05.550 --> 00:21:07.030
I could actually fight that well.

00:21:09.550 --> 00:21:10.480
I guess

00:21:11.590 --> 00:21:13.000
that's the power of love.

00:21:13.880 --> 00:21:14.720
Right?

00:21:37.270 --> 00:21:38.200
Xiaoxi,

00:21:39.000 --> 00:21:39.840
I

00:21:40.030 --> 00:21:41.590
really have to call you out on this.

00:21:42.590 --> 00:21:43.640
Tell me,

00:21:44.830 --> 00:21:46.960
how many boyfriends
are you dating at the same time?

00:21:55.070 --> 00:21:55.920
Huh?

00:21:55.920 --> 00:21:57.920
Guan, this person...

00:21:57.920 --> 00:21:58.960
You can leave first.

00:21:59.350 --> 00:22:00.550
I need a word with Guan.

00:22:01.640 --> 00:22:02.880
But she...

00:22:03.110 --> 00:22:03.960
It's fine.

00:22:04.270 --> 00:22:05.240
Wait for me outside.

00:22:07.640 --> 00:22:08.480
Go on.

00:22:14.550 --> 00:22:15.720
I miss those days

00:22:15.830 --> 00:22:17.110
in the UK.

00:22:17.160 --> 00:22:18.240
So happy.

00:22:19.030 --> 00:22:19.880
Yeah.

00:22:20.380 --> 00:22:21.240
I still remember

00:22:21.270 --> 00:22:23.350
we'd ride bikes around the town,

00:22:23.550 --> 00:22:25.270
then fly kites in the fields.

00:22:25.360 --> 00:22:26.240
We also went to

00:22:26.310 --> 00:22:28.000
my first concert together.

00:22:30.350 --> 00:22:31.790
Those days felt like

00:22:32.110 --> 00:22:33.480
a long,

00:22:33.880 --> 00:22:35.070
relaxing winter vacation.

00:22:37.070 --> 00:22:38.270
Shall we go again?

00:22:39.640 --> 00:22:40.880
Sure, someday.

00:22:42.240 --> 00:22:43.350
But I wonder if Du Mian

00:22:43.590 --> 00:22:45.270
will come with us then.

00:22:47.160 --> 00:22:48.270
I'm so grateful

00:22:48.510 --> 00:22:50.240
I met you and Du Mian

00:22:50.590 --> 00:22:51.790
during my hardest time.

00:22:54.310 --> 00:22:55.550
I've always wanted to ask

00:22:55.830 --> 00:22:57.030
why did you two break up?

00:23:00.640 --> 00:23:01.590
It was my fault.

00:23:03.880 --> 00:23:05.110
I fell for someone else.

00:23:06.550 --> 00:23:07.640
When did that happen?

00:23:09.550 --> 00:23:11.070
The first time I met you.

00:23:13.830 --> 00:23:15.550
Were you just playing me for a fool?

00:23:19.550 --> 00:23:20.400
What if?

00:23:20.960 --> 00:23:21.960
What if it works?

00:23:23.030 --> 00:23:24.110
Gotta try, right?

00:23:25.110 --> 00:23:26.310
So you're calling me stupid.

00:23:27.270 --> 00:23:28.110
I wouldn't dare.

00:23:29.820 --> 00:23:31.480
You're afraid I'll threaten you,
aren't you?

00:23:32.310 --> 00:23:33.790
Take it as me being petty.

00:23:34.920 --> 00:23:36.270
No one else knows,

00:23:37.070 --> 00:23:38.720
but you should understand
my difficulties.

00:23:40.240 --> 00:23:41.110
I get it.

00:23:42.880 --> 00:23:44.200
Guan, don't stress.

00:23:44.790 --> 00:23:45.640
I'll help you.

00:23:50.590 --> 00:23:51.640
Changed your mind?

00:23:52.170 --> 00:23:53.720
I'll pass along everything you wanna say

00:23:53.880 --> 00:23:55.310
to my boyfriend, right now.

00:23:56.110 --> 00:23:57.000
Right now.

00:23:57.620 --> 00:23:59.480
Whatever the outcome,
I'll take responsibility.

00:24:00.270 --> 00:24:01.110
No need to trouble you.

00:24:09.270 --> 00:24:11.400
I know he's extremely good to me.

00:24:12.860 --> 00:24:14.830
He chased me from junior high
all the way abroad.

00:24:16.000 --> 00:24:18.070
He's so caring and attentive.

00:24:18.510 --> 00:24:20.000
I admit I was really moved.

00:24:21.720 --> 00:24:23.070
I thought he was the one.

00:24:24.830 --> 00:24:27.240
But right after I accepted him,
you showed up.

00:24:29.110 --> 00:24:30.110
That's when I realized

00:24:30.160 --> 00:24:31.510
being moved isn't love.

00:24:32.240 --> 00:24:33.480
My crush came too late.

00:24:33.590 --> 00:24:34.550
Alright.

00:24:35.160 --> 00:24:36.240
I told you last time.

00:24:36.400 --> 00:24:37.480
I have a girlfriend now.

00:24:37.490 --> 00:24:38.360
Why tell me?

00:24:38.480 --> 00:24:39.720
I know.

00:24:40.070 --> 00:24:41.400
Just let me finish, okay?

00:24:42.720 --> 00:24:44.400
I've kept this buried inside
for so long.

00:24:44.900 --> 00:24:46.830
I don't wanna ruin
the three of our relationship.

00:24:47.110 --> 00:24:48.590
Back when we lived together,

00:24:49.550 --> 00:24:51.680
I was happy and scared every day.

00:24:52.300 --> 00:24:53.480
I just wanted to stare at you,

00:24:53.700 --> 00:24:55.070
but I was afraid to meet your eyes.

00:24:55.630 --> 00:24:56.830
I wanted to be alone with you,

00:24:57.160 --> 00:24:58.310
but I had to avoid suspicion.

00:24:58.590 --> 00:24:59.510
Do you know?

00:24:59.830 --> 00:25:01.000
Every time he tried to

00:25:01.170 --> 00:25:02.590
be intimate with me in front of you,

00:25:02.720 --> 00:25:03.590
I resisted so much.

00:25:03.620 --> 00:25:04.830
I was afraid you'd dislike me.

00:25:04.920 --> 00:25:06.000
Alright, enough.

00:25:10.720 --> 00:25:11.640
I'm going back.

00:25:12.000 --> 00:25:12.840
Hey.

00:25:14.440 --> 00:25:15.310
Wait a second.

00:25:15.330 --> 00:25:16.170
Get some rest early.

00:25:16.200 --> 00:25:17.070
Don't leave.

00:25:17.550 --> 00:25:18.390
Did you forget

00:25:18.400 --> 00:25:19.640
why you came?

00:25:20.510 --> 00:25:22.070
I found out everything.

00:25:23.030 --> 00:25:23.870
Some people think

00:25:23.870 --> 00:25:26.240
tests can measure love's loyalty,

00:25:26.680 --> 00:25:27.520
you know?

00:25:27.920 --> 00:25:29.550
You're going to tell Bei now?

00:25:29.650 --> 00:25:30.490
Yeah.

00:25:30.510 --> 00:25:31.590
Including what's between us?

00:25:31.920 --> 00:25:33.030
What's between us?

00:25:33.100 --> 00:25:34.020
What are you afraid of?

00:25:34.030 --> 00:25:35.030
I'm not afraid of anything.

00:25:35.100 --> 00:25:36.200
I just want you to calm down.

00:25:36.310 --> 00:25:37.400
I wanna calm down too.

00:25:37.510 --> 00:25:38.830
But you messed up the act.

00:25:39.960 --> 00:25:40.960
Now I have to

00:25:41.000 --> 00:25:41.920
tell Xiao Bei everything.

00:25:42.440 --> 00:25:43.280
And also him.

00:25:43.310 --> 00:25:44.550
He's been hiding a lot from me.

00:25:44.900 --> 00:25:46.680
It is the perfect chance
for everyone to talk it out.

00:25:47.160 --> 00:25:48.830
I just wanna have a normal relationship.

00:25:49.030 --> 00:25:50.480
I'm done with all this pain.

00:25:50.790 --> 00:25:52.070
But does it have to be right now?

00:25:53.030 --> 00:25:54.310
Why did Bei

00:25:54.590 --> 00:25:55.750
break up with his ex?

00:25:56.830 --> 00:25:57.670
You...

00:25:58.400 --> 00:25:59.510
Why are you suddenly

00:25:59.640 --> 00:26:00.720
so interested in her today?

00:26:01.550 --> 00:26:02.390
Tell me.

00:26:02.830 --> 00:26:03.830
I don't know.

00:26:03.960 --> 00:26:05.030
Did you hear something?

00:26:09.640 --> 00:26:11.030
If you want to talk, maybe not here.

00:26:11.200 --> 00:26:12.480
What if that aunt comes back

00:26:12.500 --> 00:26:13.680
asking me to appraise her bags?

00:26:13.800 --> 00:26:14.880
Come on, find another spot.

00:26:17.520 --> 00:26:18.390
Don't hold me.

00:26:18.410 --> 00:26:20.070
Slow down,
you're wearing such high heels.

00:26:38.480 --> 00:26:39.320
I'm hungry.

00:26:46.160 --> 00:26:47.160
What do you want to eat?

00:26:49.270 --> 00:26:50.160
I'll cook for you.

00:26:50.750 --> 00:26:52.240
I just heard it from someone too.

00:26:52.480 --> 00:26:53.440
You know he's

00:26:53.440 --> 00:26:54.510
not good at expressing himself.

00:26:55.000 --> 00:26:56.240
Never tells us anything.

00:26:56.720 --> 00:26:57.750
It's like...

00:26:58.430 --> 00:26:59.590
that girl really cares about money.

00:27:00.510 --> 00:27:01.750
She thought Bei was poor?

00:27:02.110 --> 00:27:03.160
Not exactly.

00:27:03.480 --> 00:27:04.880
But who doesn't want more money?

00:27:05.240 --> 00:27:06.720
Bei's a workaholic.

00:27:06.880 --> 00:27:08.270
Back in school,

00:27:08.680 --> 00:27:09.960
he sold fast food and milk tea.

00:27:10.530 --> 00:27:12.070
Made hundreds of thousands
by graduation.

00:27:12.160 --> 00:27:13.480
We poor folks

00:27:13.790 --> 00:27:14.720
couldn't keep up.

00:27:15.790 --> 00:27:16.630
And then?

00:27:16.830 --> 00:27:18.640
Then he got into the vintage bag market

00:27:18.830 --> 00:27:19.790
and made a killing.

00:27:20.400 --> 00:27:21.790
But he was still too young.

00:27:22.640 --> 00:27:23.640
Scammed by fakes,

00:27:23.680 --> 00:27:24.750
lost everything.

00:27:24.880 --> 00:27:26.790
I think that's when the girl left him.

00:27:27.400 --> 00:27:28.270
Now I get why Bei

00:27:28.350 --> 00:27:30.350
does luxury appraisal.

00:27:30.350 --> 00:27:31.210
Mm.

00:27:31.240 --> 00:27:32.920
Told you he's sharp.

00:27:33.200 --> 00:27:35.590
He went to Europe just to study it.

00:27:35.700 --> 00:27:37.400
(Zhen Guan)
Opened a company right after returning.

00:27:37.400 --> 00:27:38.880
Business was booming.

00:27:39.070 --> 00:27:40.720
Bags on the left, and bags on the right.

00:27:40.830 --> 00:27:41.670
Eh.

00:27:42.440 --> 00:27:43.680
Speaking of appraisals,

00:27:44.750 --> 00:27:46.920
you two are practically half-colleagues.

00:27:49.790 --> 00:27:51.310
Bei must've felt awful at that time.

00:27:52.640 --> 00:27:54.750
Felt awful? Who even knows.

00:27:55.160 --> 00:27:57.200
He always had that grumpy face,
no one could tell.

00:27:58.640 --> 00:28:00.070
But in these past few years,

00:28:00.200 --> 00:28:02.480
he hasn't dated much.

00:28:02.570 --> 00:28:03.470
I seriously wonder

00:28:03.480 --> 00:28:04.750
if something happened to him

00:28:04.920 --> 00:28:05.880
in the UK.

00:28:06.030 --> 00:28:07.110
I miss those days

00:28:07.200 --> 00:28:08.550
in the UK.

00:28:08.680 --> 00:28:09.550
So happy.

00:28:09.880 --> 00:28:11.270
Those days felt like

00:28:11.680 --> 00:28:13.000
a long,

00:28:13.440 --> 00:28:14.640
relaxing winter vacation.

00:28:15.000 --> 00:28:16.200
Shall we go again?

00:28:16.400 --> 00:28:17.350
Sure, someday.

00:28:17.480 --> 00:28:18.590
But I wonder if Du Mian

00:28:18.880 --> 00:28:20.400
will come with us then.

00:28:20.590 --> 00:28:21.790
I've always wanted to ask

00:28:22.160 --> 00:28:23.200
why did you two break up?

00:28:23.550 --> 00:28:24.880
I fell for someone else.

00:28:25.350 --> 00:28:26.200
When did that happen?

00:28:26.680 --> 00:28:28.400
The first time I met you.

00:28:35.720 --> 00:28:36.750
Bei said

00:28:37.800 --> 00:28:39.030
Jiang Yifan is a terrible woman.

00:28:39.480 --> 00:28:40.640
Jiang Yifan

00:28:41.350 --> 00:28:43.830
really is a hateful villain.

00:28:45.240 --> 00:28:46.440
That's why I'm scared to tell him

00:28:46.440 --> 00:28:47.550
about my past.

00:28:48.550 --> 00:28:50.240
I hope I can become

00:28:50.440 --> 00:28:52.200
the girl he dreams of.

00:28:54.400 --> 00:28:55.830
But I'm more and more afraid.

00:28:57.310 --> 00:28:58.510
I'm afraid he'll end up like

00:28:58.590 --> 00:29:00.240
that little boy in your story.

00:29:01.160 --> 00:29:02.960
If he finds out the real me,

00:29:04.160 --> 00:29:05.350
he'll be terrified

00:29:06.440 --> 00:29:08.030
and leave.

00:29:10.590 --> 00:29:11.550
So?

00:29:12.110 --> 00:29:13.590
So I wanna finish this puzzle.

00:29:14.200 --> 00:29:15.160
Face it.

00:29:16.880 --> 00:29:18.350
Hope one day I can

00:29:18.960 --> 00:29:20.640
tell him everything openly.

00:29:22.200 --> 00:29:23.480
Let him know the real me.

00:29:29.310 --> 00:29:30.150
I support you.

00:29:30.510 --> 00:29:31.350
Also…

00:29:32.100 --> 00:29:33.270
I wanna take back what I said.

00:29:34.830 --> 00:29:35.670
Which part?

00:29:35.830 --> 00:29:36.890
"Criticize the act, not the person.."

00:29:38.510 --> 00:29:39.480
The Li Xiaoxi I used to know

00:29:39.550 --> 00:29:41.140
and the Li Xiaoxi I know now.

00:29:41.140 --> 00:29:42.350
They're totally different people.

00:29:43.310 --> 00:29:44.350
She's not carefree.

00:29:44.880 --> 00:29:45.790
She doubts herself.

00:29:46.110 --> 00:29:47.070
She's not gentle either.

00:29:47.720 --> 00:29:48.680
She snaps out of nowhere.

00:29:50.510 --> 00:29:51.350
Sorry.

00:29:52.400 --> 00:29:54.160
I lost my temper today.

00:29:54.790 --> 00:29:55.960
I'll take that as an apology.

00:29:56.820 --> 00:29:57.960
Don't worry, I never hold grudges.

00:29:59.640 --> 00:30:00.550
And her?

00:30:01.240 --> 00:30:02.750
She's got countless faces.

00:30:04.110 --> 00:30:07.680
But to me,
she's still incredibly charming.

00:30:09.920 --> 00:30:10.760
A friend.

00:30:12.270 --> 00:30:13.110
So,

00:30:13.550 --> 00:30:15.750
just be yourself.

00:30:19.680 --> 00:30:20.550
Thanks.

00:30:21.260 --> 00:30:26.540
♪It's so real, you are right♪

00:30:27.460 --> 00:30:33.580
♪Could you hold me through the night♪

00:30:40.960 --> 00:30:42.080
- You're awake.
- Mm.

00:30:42.200 --> 00:30:43.880
Did I wake you with the noise?

00:30:44.310 --> 00:30:45.790
No, I was just hungry.

00:30:48.110 --> 00:30:48.950
Then,

00:30:49.750 --> 00:30:50.830
I'll pour some milk.

00:31:01.830 --> 00:31:02.750
You're so sweet.

00:31:07.510 --> 00:31:08.830
Oh, right.

00:31:09.750 --> 00:31:10.880
Got any plans today?

00:31:13.110 --> 00:31:14.510
Not really, why?

00:31:15.000 --> 00:31:17.270
After lunch, I'll take you somewhere.

00:31:19.640 --> 00:31:20.480
Mm.

00:31:23.340 --> 00:31:24.350
Let's play rock-paper-scissors.

00:31:24.510 --> 00:31:25.350
Ba… balloon.

00:31:25.680 --> 00:31:26.600
It's white.

00:31:26.720 --> 00:31:27.680
Rock-paper-scissors.

00:31:28.200 --> 00:31:29.040
Oh, you won.

00:31:30.030 --> 00:31:30.960
Alright, it's yours.

00:31:32.030 --> 00:31:32.870
Hey, hold it tight.

00:31:35.440 --> 00:31:36.400
Hi, kiddo.

00:31:36.400 --> 00:31:37.240
Want it?

00:31:37.640 --> 00:31:38.480
Want it?

00:31:53.640 --> 00:31:54.510
Careful!

00:31:54.550 --> 00:31:55.400
Let me give you a hug.

00:31:55.550 --> 00:31:56.390
Dad.

00:31:56.550 --> 00:31:57.550
Watch me.

00:32:19.640 --> 00:32:20.480
Xi.

00:32:21.240 --> 00:32:22.080
This is for you.

00:32:23.400 --> 00:32:24.640
Thanks.

00:32:26.440 --> 00:32:28.270
Sorry, I'm a bit late.

00:32:29.160 --> 00:32:30.640
No, I actually got here early.

00:32:31.720 --> 00:32:32.920
Busy day?

00:32:34.030 --> 00:32:34.880
Not really.

00:32:35.300 --> 00:32:36.350
Staff's handling the shop.

00:32:36.350 --> 00:32:37.440
So I can sneak a short break.

00:32:38.510 --> 00:32:39.380
But

00:32:39.400 --> 00:32:41.110
that trip we planned

00:32:41.310 --> 00:32:42.350
might need to be postponed.

00:32:42.520 --> 00:32:43.400
It's fine.

00:32:43.440 --> 00:32:44.750
We can travel anytime.

00:32:45.750 --> 00:32:47.160
Try the coffee here.

00:32:47.600 --> 00:32:48.680
It was just freshly ground.

00:32:48.920 --> 00:32:49.760
Thanks.

00:32:53.030 --> 00:32:53.870
How is it?

00:32:57.240 --> 00:32:58.080
Pretty good.

00:32:58.510 --> 00:33:00.200
The flavor and richness
are just my type.

00:33:02.510 --> 00:33:04.480
This coffee shop's right
by your flower shop.

00:33:04.600 --> 00:33:05.550
Do you come here often?

00:33:05.630 --> 00:33:06.470
Mm.

00:33:06.510 --> 00:33:07.350
I come here often.

00:33:08.000 --> 00:33:08.880
Do you like it?

00:33:10.700 --> 00:33:11.750
The place has a nice vibe.

00:33:12.750 --> 00:33:13.640
The coffee's good too.

00:33:15.590 --> 00:33:17.070
But this music...

00:33:18.480 --> 00:33:19.320
Not quite my thing.

00:33:19.440 --> 00:33:20.550
You're not into the music?

00:33:22.000 --> 00:33:23.480
Maybe I'm just older.

00:33:23.480 --> 00:33:24.830
I prefer something...

00:33:25.160 --> 00:33:26.400
A little softer.

00:33:26.550 --> 00:33:27.390
And then,

00:33:27.550 --> 00:33:28.550
when you listen,

00:33:28.790 --> 00:33:30.440
it calms the mood.

00:33:31.030 --> 00:33:32.110
Like...

00:33:33.590 --> 00:33:34.920
Like Those Flowers.

00:33:34.920 --> 00:33:35.780
Or New Everlasting Love.

00:33:35.790 --> 00:33:37.820
Or You Don't Live Here Anymore, or...

00:33:37.820 --> 00:33:38.700
(Those Flowers)

00:33:45.550 --> 00:33:46.390
Wait.

00:33:47.920 --> 00:33:48.760
This is...

00:33:50.680 --> 00:33:51.920
This shop's yours?

00:33:52.270 --> 00:33:53.720
Mm, it used to be.

00:33:54.590 --> 00:33:55.510
And now?

00:33:56.030 --> 00:33:56.880
Ours.

00:33:58.380 --> 00:34:00.620
♪Those flowers of mine♪

00:34:00.640 --> 00:34:01.480
Do you like it?

00:34:01.590 --> 00:34:03.000
What a big surprise!

00:34:03.000 --> 00:34:08.060
♪In every corner of my life
quietly blooming for me♪

00:34:12.960 --> 00:34:14.110
Why did you bring me here?

00:34:15.110 --> 00:34:16.400
Didn't you always want to open a

00:34:16.400 --> 00:34:17.480
photography studio?

00:34:17.920 --> 00:34:19.800
The location and layout of this place

00:34:19.960 --> 00:34:21.000
are just perfect.

00:34:21.010 --> 00:34:21.860
Oh.

00:34:21.870 --> 00:34:22.800
I checked about this place.

00:34:23.000 --> 00:34:24.480
The transfer fee alone
is a hundred grand.

00:34:24.480 --> 00:34:25.550
Not even counting renovation,

00:34:25.550 --> 00:34:26.840
labor, or equipment costs.

00:34:26.900 --> 00:34:27.740
(Prime shop transfer)

00:34:27.740 --> 00:34:28.710
Let's go.

00:34:30.040 --> 00:34:30.930
What are you doing?

00:34:30.960 --> 00:34:31.960
I forgot to tell you

00:34:33.190 --> 00:34:34.550
I already paid

00:34:34.710 --> 00:34:35.670
the transfer fee.

00:34:35.800 --> 00:34:37.630
Meeting the landlord today
to sign and pay the balance.

00:34:37.800 --> 00:34:38.880
And settle the final payment.

00:34:39.510 --> 00:34:40.590
Starting today,

00:34:47.440 --> 00:34:48.510
this shop

00:34:49.630 --> 00:34:50.550
is officially yours.

00:34:52.710 --> 00:34:53.880
Are you serious?

00:35:03.960 --> 00:35:06.630
The shop's called Capricorn Café.

00:35:07.230 --> 00:35:08.480
Does that have something to do with me?

00:35:08.880 --> 00:35:09.800
Of course.

00:35:10.000 --> 00:35:10.840
Really.

00:35:10.840 --> 00:35:13.000
It's to remember
all our countless coffee dates.

00:35:13.840 --> 00:35:15.000
Plus, I've even collected items

00:35:15.070 --> 00:35:16.760
from every café we've been to.

00:35:17.920 --> 00:35:19.400
You always surprise me.

00:35:20.440 --> 00:35:21.480
You're the one.

00:35:22.070 --> 00:35:24.360
I just found out
how good you are at fighting.

00:35:25.070 --> 00:35:26.150
You've trained before?

00:35:26.740 --> 00:35:27.590
When I was a kid,

00:35:27.590 --> 00:35:29.150
I actually practiced
martial arts for a while.

00:35:29.860 --> 00:35:30.710
Really?

00:35:30.710 --> 00:35:32.440
Yeah, I always dreamed of being a hero.

00:35:36.580 --> 00:35:38.060
(An Miu)

00:35:40.760 --> 00:35:42.400
I've already tidied up my place.

00:35:42.400 --> 00:35:44.000
Can I come over to your shop to see you?

00:35:46.840 --> 00:35:47.880
Oh, by the way.

00:35:49.440 --> 00:35:50.320
Lipstick.

00:35:51.000 --> 00:35:51.960
It's been delivered to you.

00:35:51.960 --> 00:35:52.800
Thanks.

00:36:00.590 --> 00:36:01.630
Oh, by the way.

00:36:02.280 --> 00:36:03.760
Besides this café,

00:36:04.000 --> 00:36:05.440
I have something else to tell you.

00:36:06.360 --> 00:36:07.200
What is it?

00:36:09.480 --> 00:36:11.000
I used to invest in a

00:36:11.320 --> 00:36:12.400
- women's club.
- This is...

00:36:13.920 --> 00:36:15.000
Bei?

00:36:16.960 --> 00:36:17.800
Oh.

00:36:18.220 --> 00:36:20.510
Look how excited you are.
Didn't expect me to show up, huh?

00:36:23.320 --> 00:36:25.030
Don't worry, I've changed my mind.

00:36:29.030 --> 00:36:30.230
Hello, Mr. Bei.

00:36:30.510 --> 00:36:31.350
Hello.

00:36:31.800 --> 00:36:33.510
Xiaoxi talks about you all the time.

00:36:33.920 --> 00:36:35.800
Now I see why

00:36:35.920 --> 00:36:37.480
she's always been so on edge

00:36:37.960 --> 00:36:38.960
about me meeting you.

00:36:40.760 --> 00:36:41.610
Ah.

00:36:41.670 --> 00:36:43.960
She was scared I'd confront you.

00:36:44.920 --> 00:36:47.590
She used to help me run a women's club,

00:36:47.840 --> 00:36:49.110
but quit.

00:36:50.070 --> 00:36:51.110
After she started dating,

00:36:53.880 --> 00:36:54.720
this...

00:36:54.960 --> 00:36:55.840
This is...

00:36:56.070 --> 00:36:57.110
Let me introduce her.

00:36:57.480 --> 00:36:59.030
This is my long-time friend.

00:36:59.360 --> 00:37:00.200
Guan.

00:37:00.480 --> 00:37:01.440
Nice to meet you, Guan.

00:37:01.710 --> 00:37:02.710
Hey, sorry about that.

00:37:02.880 --> 00:37:04.630
I probably took up too much
of Xiaoxi's time

00:37:04.800 --> 00:37:05.960
and messed with your business.

00:37:06.360 --> 00:37:08.190
No, actually,

00:37:08.550 --> 00:37:10.760
I've been sorting out this café lately,

00:37:11.360 --> 00:37:12.480
so that's why I fell behind.

00:37:13.840 --> 00:37:14.680
Mr. Bei,

00:37:14.880 --> 00:37:17.480
could I borrow your girlfriend
for half a day?

00:37:17.710 --> 00:37:19.440
We need to wrap up some loose ends

00:37:19.670 --> 00:37:20.800
about her leaving the company.

00:37:21.110 --> 00:37:21.960
Is that okay?

00:37:22.550 --> 00:37:23.710
Ah, of course.

00:37:23.790 --> 00:37:24.650
But Guan,

00:37:24.710 --> 00:37:25.880
I have a few words to say to Xiaoxi.

00:37:26.280 --> 00:37:27.510
Could you wait a minute?

00:37:27.840 --> 00:37:29.030
Of course.

00:37:29.920 --> 00:37:31.630
I'll wait in the private room.

00:37:31.840 --> 00:37:32.680
Okay.

00:37:33.550 --> 00:37:34.390
See you.

00:37:42.320 --> 00:37:43.960
Xiaoxi, come on, sit down.

00:37:48.670 --> 00:37:50.760
So, there's something
I need to tell you.

00:37:51.800 --> 00:37:54.800
When I was studying abroad,

00:37:55.550 --> 00:37:56.800
I had a roommate.

00:37:57.030 --> 00:37:58.110
She just came back from overseas.

00:37:58.280 --> 00:37:59.760
I want to introduce her to you.

00:38:00.320 --> 00:38:01.160
Sure.

00:38:01.880 --> 00:38:02.760
Is it a guy or a girl?

00:38:03.840 --> 00:38:05.110
Uh, a girl.

00:38:05.480 --> 00:38:06.800
But she's like a sister to me.

00:38:07.400 --> 00:38:08.240
Oh.

00:38:08.760 --> 00:38:09.670
A sister.

00:38:11.110 --> 00:38:12.670
No, back then it was like this.

00:38:12.840 --> 00:38:14.760
I failed at my business here.

00:38:14.960 --> 00:38:15.960
Plus

00:38:16.960 --> 00:38:18.590
some pretty rough stuff happened.

00:38:19.070 --> 00:38:20.320
So I went abroad to study.

00:38:20.630 --> 00:38:23.110
During that time, I was really

00:38:23.670 --> 00:38:24.630
upset, you know.

00:38:25.030 --> 00:38:26.110
Grateful to

00:38:26.110 --> 00:38:27.510
her and her boyfriend.

00:38:27.880 --> 00:38:28.880
They were my roommates,

00:38:29.110 --> 00:38:31.230
got me through the hardest time.

00:38:31.960 --> 00:38:34.150
Even though
she broke up with her boyfriend,

00:38:34.440 --> 00:38:35.310
we still get along,

00:38:35.360 --> 00:38:36.630
just like family.

00:38:36.960 --> 00:38:38.190
- So now I...
- I trust you.

00:38:42.760 --> 00:38:45.190
Why are you stuttering? You're nervous.

00:38:45.190 --> 00:38:46.550
No. Just afraid

00:38:46.880 --> 00:38:48.000
you'll misunderstand.

00:38:48.920 --> 00:38:50.710
Wish we'd met earlier.

00:38:51.960 --> 00:38:52.920
It's not too late now.

00:38:53.190 --> 00:38:54.070
It's perfect timing.

00:38:58.400 --> 00:38:59.960
Go ahead and focus on your work first.

00:39:00.590 --> 00:39:02.150
If you've got things to handle at work,

00:39:02.150 --> 00:39:03.150
don't worry about me.

00:39:03.670 --> 00:39:04.590
I don't want you to

00:39:04.590 --> 00:39:05.710
give up anything for me.

00:39:06.710 --> 00:39:08.280
Okay, I know.

00:39:09.070 --> 00:39:09.920
Alright, I'll go.

00:39:09.960 --> 00:39:11.000
Text me when you're done.

00:39:11.000 --> 00:39:11.840
Yeah.

00:39:16.030 --> 00:39:17.030
- Bye.
- Bye.

00:39:35.030 --> 00:39:36.550
Have you been following me?

00:39:38.880 --> 00:39:40.550
I knew you'd think that.

00:39:41.710 --> 00:39:42.590
In your mind,

00:39:42.590 --> 00:39:43.920
is that really who I am?

00:39:46.760 --> 00:39:48.320
You showed up at the perfect time.

00:39:49.440 --> 00:39:50.710
I know you inside out.

00:39:51.920 --> 00:39:53.280
Once you get stubborn,

00:39:53.340 --> 00:39:54.480
you stop caring about anything.

00:39:54.630 --> 00:39:56.030
You'll just tell him everything.

00:39:56.820 --> 00:39:58.150
Have you thought about the outcome?

00:39:58.670 --> 00:39:59.960
With some things,

00:40:00.230 --> 00:40:02.960
guys can be more petty than girls.

00:40:03.800 --> 00:40:04.880
Even if he knows,

00:40:05.030 --> 00:40:06.400
and still wants to be with you,

00:40:08.190 --> 00:40:09.230
can you be sure

00:40:09.760 --> 00:40:11.960
of what he's truly thinking?

00:40:14.960 --> 00:40:16.360
If he can't accept it,

00:40:17.440 --> 00:40:18.760
I deserve to face it.

00:40:21.190 --> 00:40:23.800
Honestly, I have no idea
what to say to you.

00:40:24.400 --> 00:40:25.760
Too confident

00:40:26.590 --> 00:40:27.710
or just naive?

00:40:34.320 --> 00:40:36.630
I canceled everything else.

00:40:37.150 --> 00:40:38.110
I have a younger sister.

00:40:38.280 --> 00:40:39.840
Can you meet her this afternoon?

00:40:40.800 --> 00:40:41.640
Just a meet-up.

00:40:41.920 --> 00:40:43.110
No other requests.

00:40:50.200 --> 00:40:52.799
♪I'll admit♪

00:40:52.800 --> 00:40:56.839
♪My back is faced against the wall♪

00:40:57.720 --> 00:41:01.586
♪There's nothing that
I wouldn't try to do♪

00:41:01.611 --> 00:41:05.799
♪For this feeling to have you♪

00:41:06.080 --> 00:41:08.279
♪I'll resist♪

00:41:08.600 --> 00:41:10.614
♪Your gaze, your lips♪

00:41:10.639 --> 00:41:12.799
♪Your touches again♪

00:41:13.680 --> 00:41:17.660
♪There's no one that
I wouldn't try to fool♪

00:41:17.685 --> 00:41:20.719
♪For an image of you♪

00:41:21.720 --> 00:41:24.159
♪Take my hand again♪

00:41:24.160 --> 00:41:25.919
♪Take my mind again♪

00:41:26.000 --> 00:41:29.359
♪Break into my heart again♪

00:41:29.760 --> 00:41:31.937
♪I'm falling out again♪

00:41:31.962 --> 00:41:33.799
♪I'm on my knees again♪

00:41:33.800 --> 00:41:37.639
♪To beg for the truth♪

00:41:39.480 --> 00:41:43.639
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:41:43.640 --> 00:41:48.639
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:41:49.000 --> 00:41:51.959
♪I thought it had came from
below us♪

00:41:52.040 --> 00:41:55.439
♪Did it come from above♪

00:41:55.520 --> 00:41:59.279
♪Tell me the secret of love♪

00:41:59.520 --> 00:42:04.599
♪Is that the secret to love♪

00:42:05.000 --> 00:42:07.439
♪Is it violent or warming, entrancing♪

00:42:07.440 --> 00:42:11.879
♪This secret of love♪